---
title: Swedish-Style Turkey Meatballs with Creamy Gravy and Buttery Broccoli
description: Skip a trip to a certain Scandinavian shop and make these DIY Swedish meatballs at home! Soften seasoned breadcrumbs with a bit of milk for extra-tender results.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1006_W19_CA_RB154969-6_Main_low-7b6add0e.jpg
